Abstract: Joshua Davis, high school student from Montclair, NJ, has taken front page of newspaper for last 1,000 days of 1900's and created origami cranes for collection that he says will symbolize end of 1,000 years; his plan, after completing 1,000th crane, is to donate them to museum; photo (M)

LeadParagraph: Joshua Davis, 17, has been counting down each of the 1900's last 1,000 days by scanning the front page of a daily newspaper.
